<div style="padding:0em 0.25em"><b><a href="/wiki/Byzantine_army" title="Byzantine army">Byzantine army</a></b> (<a href="/wiki/Late_Roman_army" title="Late Roman army">Late Roman army</a> → <a href="/wiki/East_Roman_army" title="East Roman army">East Roman army</a> → Middle Byzantine army → <a href="/wiki/Komnenian_army" title="Komnenian army">Komnenian army</a> → <a href="/wiki/Palaiologan_army" title="Palaiologan army">Palaiologan army</a>): <a href="/wiki/Byzantine_battle_tactics" title="Byzantine battle tactics">Battle tactics</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Byzantine_military_manuals" title="Byzantine military manuals">Military manuals</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/w/index.php?title=Byzantine_siege_warfare&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Byzantine siege warfare (page does not exist)">Siege warfare</a> <span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Category:Wars_involving_the_Byzantine_Empire" title="Category:Wars involving the Byzantine Empire">Wars</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Category:Byzantine_generals" title="Category:Byzantine generals">Generals</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Foederati" title="Foederati">Foederati</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Bucellarii" title="Bucellarii" class="mw-redirect">Bucellarii</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Tagma_(military)" title="Tagma (military)">Tagmata</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Category:Byzantine_mercenaries" title="Category:Byzantine mercenaries">Mercenaries</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Varangian_Guard" title="Varangian Guard" class="mw-redirect">Varangian Guard</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Akritoi" title="Akritoi">Akritoi</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Pronoia" title="Pronoia">Pronoia</a><br />
<b><a href="/wiki/Byzantine_navy" title="Byzantine navy">Byzantine navy</a></b>: <a href="/wiki/Dromon" title="Dromon">Dromon</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <strong class="selflink">Greek fire</strong><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Category:Byzantine_admirals" title="Category:Byzantine admirals">Admirals</a></div>
